    "description": "本課程介紹職涯發展的意義與重要性，增進學生對自我的瞭解，提升學生對工作世界的認識，並協助學生發展適切的生涯目標，以及培養提升學生的職涯發展能力。",
    "prerequisites": "",
    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.職涯的意義與內涵<br>2.職涯成熟度<br>3.認識自己-我的興趣<br>4.認識自己-我的性格特質<br>5.認識自己-我的需求與價值觀<br>6.認識自己-我的能力及優勢條件<br>7.自我觀點及人格成熟度<br>8.認識工作世界-幼兒園及其發展趨勢<br>9.認識工作世界-托嬰中心及其發展趨勢<br>10.認識工作世界-兒童相關產業<br>11.認識工作世界-工作世界未來的發展趨勢<br>12.職涯發展能力的培養<br>",
        "en": "1. The meaning and connotation of career <br>2. Career Maturity<br>3. Know myself - my interests<br>4. Know myself - my personality traits<br>5. Know myself - my needs and values<br>6. Know myself - my abilities and advantages<br>7. Self-viewpoints and personality maturity<br>8. Understanding the world of work-kindergartens and their development trends<br>9. Understanding the world of work - babysitting centers and their development trends<br>10. Understanding the world of work - children-related industries<br>11. Understanding the world of work - the future development trend of the world of work<br>12. Cultivation of career development ability<br><br>"
